videos.description: The Longhorns move the ball around and eventually Matt Coleman finishes with the lay-in.
videos.headline: Texas uses great ball movement to take lead

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba splits the defenders and finishes with a big dunk for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Mo Bamba throws down big one-handed dunk for Texas

videos.description: Texas goes into halftime with a 29-24 lead over No.  8 Texas Tech after Mohamed Bamba throws down a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Texas ends half on emphatic note with Mo Bama dunk

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski drives down the baseline and throws down a dunk while drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Texas keeps it going with Osetkowski dunk and-1

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba blocks Niem Stevenson's shot from behind and passes Joel Embiid for 4th most blocked shots by a freshman in Big 12 history.
videos.headline: Mo Bamba rejects Stevenson with record-breaking block

videos.description: Zhaire Smith works his way around Mohamed Bamba and finishes with a dunk to cut the Longhorns' lead.
videos.headline: Texas Tech answers with a Smith slam
